highlights.text: Sơn Tùng M-TP has the most spots on Top Songs Vietnam. “Buông Đôi Tay Nhau Ra” is the highest at #12.
“Lặng” by Rhymastic is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Vietnam, up 40 spots at #108.
“Âm Thầm Bên Em” by Sơn Tùng M-TP has been on Top Songs Vietnam the longest, at 1724 days straight.
